name: Gscraft
tagline: The official website for the GScraft minecraft server. Including a list of the players, plot summaries and MOAR!
body:
# GScraft
GScraft is a minecraft server run by the YouTubers ZEPHrom and CAldeo. It is a private vanilla survival server with a fair trade system to get spawn eggs intended for our group of friends.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
